\n```\nWhere submit/unlink visibility is toggled based on `hasLink`.\n\n### Context\n\n```ts\ninterface LinkFormContextValue {\n  inputRef: React.RefObject<HTMLInputElement | null>;\n  inputValue: string;\n  setInputValue: (value: string) => void;\n  hasLink: boolean;\n  currentHref: string;\n  handleSubmit: (e: React.FormEvent) => void;\n  handleUnlink: (e: React.MouseEvent) => void;\n  element: 'link' | 'button' | 'image';\n}\n```\n\nExport: `LinkForm`, `LinkFormInput`, `LinkFormSubmit`, `LinkFormUnlink`.\n\nUse `'use client'` directive. Write every line. No placeholders.",
